config LIN_SKELETON
	bool "LIN Skeleton Driver"
	default y
	depends on DT_HAS_ZEPHYR_LIN_SKELETON_ENABLED
	help
	  Enable the LIN Skeleton driver for testing and development purposes.
	  This is a minimal implementation that does not interact with real hardware.
	  It is intended for use in simulation or as a template for developing new LIN drivers.
